899
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem čovjeku,

900
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] blagoslovi svoje dijete pri odlaska u vrtić,

901
00:42:21,239 --> 00:42:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] i on je onda intervenirao

902
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:22,780
[SPEAKER_01] i rekli su,

903
00:42:22,780 --> 00:42:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] ok, dijete ne mora biti u programu jogi,

904
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] bit će u drugoj prostoriji,

905
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali sam je taj prostor,

906
00:42:29,059 --> 00:42:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, ako se to država joga,

907
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa čovječe,

908
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,940
[SPEAKER_01] ja kad dođem u Hercegovornu,

909
00:42:33,940 --> 00:42:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja prodišem,

910
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] ja gledam reći,

911
00:42:36,639 --> 00:42:39,019
[SPEAKER_01] kao što u Međugorju,

912
00:42:39,019 --> 00:42:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođeš,

913
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] udišeš tu svetost,

914
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer ona je u zraku,

915
00:42:41,659 --> 00:42:42,400
[SPEAKER_01] ona je u okruženju,

916
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] ona je u prostoru,

917
00:42:43,239 --> 00:42:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Boži duh,

918
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] sve,

919
00:42:44,639 --> 00:42:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] sve obuhvaća,

920
00:42:46,579 --> 00:42:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] a tako i na džavoski.

921
00:42:49,179 --> 00:42:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mu se mi klanjamo,

922
00:42:50,380 --> 00:42:50,900
[SPEAKER_01] naravno,

923
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:53,179
[SPEAKER_01] i zato mi blagoslivljamo naše kuće

924
00:42:53,179 --> 00:42:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] i da nam Boži duh dođe,

925
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] da bude prisutan na našim domovima.

926
00:42:56,880 --> 00:43:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno da je poteškoća,

927
00:43:00,019 --> 00:43:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] tu je joga u toj prostoriji

928
00:43:01,559 --> 00:43:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] i ti ulaziš tu.

929
00:43:02,500 --> 00:43:03,679
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da nije ugodno,

930
00:43:03,679 --> 00:43:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da nije dobro,

931
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim blagoslovi,

932
00:43:05,239 --> 00:43:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] izmoli zašto nad svojim djetetom,

933
00:43:07,260 --> 00:43:08,599
[SPEAKER_01] ako nemaš drugog rešenja,

934
00:43:08,599 --> 00:43:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] ako imaš pokušaj,

935
00:43:09,500 --> 00:43:11,099
[SPEAKER_01] slati možda u neki drugi vrtić

936
00:43:11,099 --> 00:43:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] ili negdje drugo.

937
00:43:12,500 --> 00:43:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nadam da će možda nekaj gore

938
00:43:13,780 --> 00:43:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] i otvoriti se neke katoličke vrtići,

939
00:43:17,219 --> 00:43:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] škole ili nešto takvo,

940
00:43:18,500 --> 00:43:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] možda ima,

941
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] nisam čuo,

942
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:23,679
[SPEAKER_01] gdje će se širiti samo vjerska poruka,

943
00:43:23,679 --> 00:43:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] poruka evanđelja.

944
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo, sad za sada situacija je teška,

945
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] u školama imaju muški vjese,

946
00:43:29,940 --> 00:43:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] ženski vjese i srednji.

947
00:43:31,039 --> 00:43:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ti,

948
00:43:32,860 --> 00:43:34,219
[SPEAKER_01] nažalost,

949
00:43:34,219 --> 00:43:35,900
[SPEAKER_01] meni je zaista žao,

950
00:43:35,900 --> 00:43:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] žao,

951
00:43:36,659 --> 00:43:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] ali takva je situacija.

952
00:43:39,780 --> 00:43:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno je takva.

953
00:43:40,760 --> 00:43:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi gore idu

954
00:43:42,179 --> 00:43:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] u potrazi

955
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] za nekim financijskim,

956
00:43:45,800 --> 00:43:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći dobitom,

957
00:43:47,420 --> 00:43:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] profitom,

958
00:43:48,800 --> 00:43:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali izgube puno važnije stvari.

959
00:43:51,579 --> 00:43:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

960
00:43:52,619 --> 00:43:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne morate ljudi,

961
00:43:54,900 --> 00:43:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte ići nigdje vani,

962
00:43:56,159 --> 00:43:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

963
00:43:57,159 --> 00:43:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] najbitnije je ono što u vašem životu,

964
00:43:59,940 --> 00:44:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] što zapravo vas formira kao osobu,

965
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] samo gospodin.

966
00:44:02,820 --> 00:44:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može vas formirati ni novac,

967
00:44:05,239 --> 00:44:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] ni stan,

968
00:44:06,139 --> 00:44:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] ni kuća,

969
00:44:07,099 --> 00:44:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] ni tiko drugi.

970
00:44:07,920 --> 00:44:10,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ako želite živjeti,

971
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] slobodno živjeti,

972
00:44:12,099 --> 00:44:13,760
[SPEAKER_01] evanđelje živjeti po Božijemu,

973
00:44:13,760 --> 00:44:15,019
[SPEAKER_01] živjeti u miru,

974
00:44:15,019 --> 00:44:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] koji nam Hristus krsli donosi,

975
00:44:16,719 --> 00:44:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno,

976
00:44:17,980 --> 00:44:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne trčimo za prolaznim dobima.

977
00:44:19,960 --> 00:44:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, samo tražite na nebeska.

978
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, još, vica ska je nekako,

979
00:44:24,719 --> 00:44:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] kao i cijela Evropa,

980
00:44:26,159 --> 00:44:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] počupala svoje kršćanske korjene,

981
00:44:28,900 --> 00:44:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] na kojima izrasla.

982
00:44:30,199 --> 00:44:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Na Švicarska ima i brojne svece,

983
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] još, mi smo bili u svetište njihovog

984
00:44:35,159 --> 00:44:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] nacionalnog zaštnjika.

985
00:44:36,519 --> 00:44:39,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bruder Klaus il sveti Nikola von Fluev,

986
00:44:39,679 --> 00:44:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] koliko velik svec, koliko je on sedamnijesil nešto godina živio samo u Neuharistiji.

987
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, to je začuđujuće.

988
00:44:47,440 --> 00:44:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] I kad su bili ratovi,

989
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] ima tamo jedna freska u crkvi,

990
00:44:51,300 --> 00:44:55,719
[SPEAKER_01] evo, baš smo nas dvojica išli kad si ti bio gore kod mene.

991
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam isto kada prvi put posjetio to svetište.

992
00:44:58,619 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je baš, baš, baš zanimljiv svetac.

993
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,739
[SPEAKER_01] Bruder Klaus, kako ga zovu,

994
00:45:05,739 --> 00:45:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] on je bio oženjen,

995
00:45:07,340 --> 00:45:08,820
[SPEAKER_01] imao je desetara djece

996
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:11,980
[SPEAKER_01] i odučio se posvetiti Bogu.

997
00:45:11,980 --> 00:45:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno, crkva mu je dopustila,

998
00:45:14,699 --> 00:45:16,679
[SPEAKER_01] kad su djeza stasala

999
00:45:16,679 --> 00:45:19,139
[SPEAKER_01] i uz dopuštenje, naravno, njegove supruge,

1000
00:45:19,139 --> 00:45:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] da posveti svoj život Bogu.

1001
00:45:20,920 --> 00:45:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] Osituo je takav poziv.

1002
00:45:22,039 --> 00:45:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] I živio je, evo, što si ti rekao,

1003
00:45:24,519 --> 00:45:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] više od 15, među 15 i 20 godina,

1004
00:45:26,760 --> 00:45:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ne znam točno,

1005
00:45:27,559 --> 00:45:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] samo Deuharistije.

1006
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,320
[SPEAKER_01] A sam mislite tu svetost.

1007
00:45:31,320 --> 00:45:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je čudesno.

1008
00:45:32,539 --> 00:45:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Čudesno.

1009
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] I kad smo bili u tom svetištu,

1010
00:45:37,480 --> 00:45:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo očekivali sad, ti znaš kako su u nas svetišta,

1011
00:45:39,780 --> 00:45:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo tako, nekog velikog sveca,

1012
00:45:41,639 --> 00:45:43,059
[SPEAKER_01] očekuješ neku veliku crkvu,

1013
00:45:43,059 --> 00:45:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] baš organizirano, okolo, sve lijepo, uredno,

1014
00:45:46,800 --> 00:45:48,320
[SPEAKER_01] prostor za molitvu,

1015
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] jedva smo našli, sjećaš se?

1016
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] Blunjali smo po onim brdima,

1017
00:45:52,559 --> 00:45:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] tražeći mala kolibica,

1018
00:45:54,920 --> 00:45:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] evo, kažu, tu je,

1019
00:45:56,559 --> 00:45:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] tu je, vidjeli smo ono kuću gdje on živio.

1020
00:45:58,579 --> 00:46:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] Koliba je doslo imala dva prozora.

1021
00:46:00,159 --> 00:46:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan koje gleda u crku,

1022
00:46:01,960 --> 00:46:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] a koju smo ljudi napravili,

1023
00:46:03,900 --> 00:46:05,559
[SPEAKER_00] drugi gdje je primao ljude.

1024
00:46:05,619 --> 00:46:07,179
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, tako je, jednostavno,

1025
00:46:07,179 --> 00:46:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] nadam se, evo, da će se malo više proširiti štovanje

1026
00:46:10,139 --> 00:46:12,519
[SPEAKER_01] prema tom velikom, velikom, velikom svecu,

1027
00:46:12,519 --> 00:46:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji je, evo, ali njega zaista

1028
00:46:14,239 --> 00:46:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] u Švicarskoj

1029
00:46:16,519 --> 00:46:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] štuje narod, zaista ga štuje,

1030
00:46:18,380 --> 00:46:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne onako kako bi trebao,

1031
00:46:19,900 --> 00:46:21,780
[SPEAKER_01] ali oni koji su pobožni,

1032
00:46:21,780 --> 00:46:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] mole se njemu zagovor,

1033
00:46:23,559 --> 00:46:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer je veliki svetac,

1034
00:46:25,420 --> 00:46:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] evo, švicarski nacionalni svetac,

1035
00:46:27,539 --> 00:46:29,719
[SPEAKER_01] i oni vjeruju zaista da kroz njegove molitve,

1036
00:46:29,719 --> 00:46:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer evo, kad je okolo buktio rat

1037
00:46:31,579 --> 00:46:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] u svim državama Europi,

1038
00:46:33,199 --> 00:46:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] oni su se molili,

1039
00:46:33,980 --> 00:46:35,840
[SPEAKER_01] i zaista Švicarska nije, evo,

1040
00:46:35,840 --> 00:46:37,179
[SPEAKER_01] dodirnuta, okrznuta,

1041
00:46:37,179 --> 00:46:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] i ljudi vjeruju da je to njegov zagovor,

1042
00:46:40,019 --> 00:46:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] tako da bio je veliki svetac,

1043
00:46:41,639 --> 00:46:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] i evo,

1044
00:46:42,659 --> 00:46:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] sveti Nikola,

1045
00:46:44,179 --> 00:46:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] Bruder, Klause,

1046
00:46:45,599 --> 00:46:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] moli se, evo, za sve nas,

1047
00:46:48,340 --> 00:46:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] pozornost za svoj švicarski narod.

1048
00:46:50,659 --> 00:46:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ovdje u Hercegni,

1049
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] pa možda počesto i,

1050
00:46:54,800 --> 00:46:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] nismo ni svjestni,

1051
00:46:56,760 --> 00:46:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] a i pomalo i nezahvalni za sve ovo,

1052
00:46:58,599 --> 00:47:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] što ovdje mi imamo,

1053
00:47:00,039 --> 00:47:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo je, pa nekoj,

1054
00:47:01,739 --> 00:47:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] duhovna privilegija sve što mi imamo,

1055
00:47:04,019 --> 00:47:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] kad pogledamo to gore siromaštvo u Švicarskoj.

1056
00:47:07,360 --> 00:47:09,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, baš duhovna privilegija,

1057
00:47:09,340 --> 00:47:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] to si jako, jako lijepo rekao,

1058
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj, ali,

1059
00:47:12,739 --> 00:47:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] tek kad odeš van, to shvatiš.

1060
00:47:14,420 --> 00:47:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja prvi,

1061
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:18,639
[SPEAKER_01] ja nisam razumio koliko je ovdje blago i ljepota,

1062
00:47:18,639 --> 00:47:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] dok ne dođeš.

1063
00:47:19,579 --> 00:47:21,159
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vidiš nekad,

1064
00:47:21,159 --> 00:47:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] zašto i naši ljudi,

1065
00:47:22,380 --> 00:47:24,179
[SPEAKER_01] ja da čekaju neka hodočašća,

1066
00:47:24,179 --> 00:47:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] da malo pobjegnu,

1067
00:47:25,699 --> 00:47:27,940
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ja prvi,

1068
00:47:27,940 --> 00:47:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] sada, kad dođeš ovamo,

1069
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] malo preko ljeta na odmor,

1070
00:47:31,539 --> 00:47:33,480
[SPEAKER_01] i odeš u Međugorje,

1071
00:47:33,480 --> 00:47:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] i sad susretiš te strance,

1072
00:47:36,119 --> 00:47:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] međugorje ima trenut na evo sa gore živim.

1073
00:47:37,980 --> 00:47:40,219
[SPEAKER_01] I tek sad svačaš,

1074
00:47:40,219 --> 00:47:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] zašto je uopće

1075
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] toliko ljudi tu u Međugorju?

1076
00:47:44,199 --> 00:47:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto su tolki brojni stranci došli?

1077
00:47:47,019 --> 00:47:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su žedni Boga.

1078
00:47:48,619 --> 00:47:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su žedni Boga,

1079
00:47:50,380 --> 00:47:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] a gore je teško naći izvor.

1080
00:47:52,760 --> 00:47:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ja zato se nadam

1081
00:47:54,679 --> 00:47:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] da će se, evo,

1082
00:47:56,059 --> 00:47:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] što više pokrenuti moletvenih zajednica,

1083
00:47:58,739 --> 00:48:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] moletvenih skupina, grupa,

1084
00:48:00,579 --> 00:48:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] frame, mladih, svih,

1085
00:48:02,539 --> 00:48:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] jer kad se takve grupe ujedinjuju,

1086
00:48:05,619 --> 00:48:06,679
[SPEAKER_01] kad vidi da ima nas više.

1087
00:48:06,679 --> 00:48:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, teško ti je nekad nešto,

1088
00:48:09,079 --> 00:48:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] svi trče tamo gdje ima ljudi.

1089
00:48:11,340 --> 00:48:12,260
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo takvi.

1090
00:48:12,260 --> 00:48:14,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bi niko sam nešto učinio,

1091
00:48:14,199 --> 00:48:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] ne bi niko sam nešto pokrenuo.

1092
00:48:15,679 --> 00:48:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je to nezgodno.

1093
00:48:17,159 --> 00:48:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] A ovdje imaš, možeš izabrat ne samo u Hercegovini,

1094
00:48:20,500 --> 00:48:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] Zagreb, pa imaš na izbor moletvenih zajednica,

1095
00:48:23,820 --> 00:48:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ko želiš priključit se.

1096
00:48:25,079 --> 00:48:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] A ako želiš rasti,

1097
00:48:26,539 --> 00:48:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] odnosu zbog gospodina,

1098
00:48:28,079 --> 00:48:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] naravno trebati odsobni odnos,

1099
00:48:30,199 --> 00:48:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] ali zajednica je jako važna.

1100
00:48:31,679 --> 00:48:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] Zajednica je jako važna.

1101
00:48:33,139 --> 00:48:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, zato sam upravo gore u Švjetskoj našoj emisiji,

1102
00:48:36,619 --> 00:48:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] rekao je, prvo sam krenuo sa tim susretima za mlade,

1103
00:48:40,860 --> 00:48:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] i vidim, ajde, napredu je dobro,

1104
00:48:42,940 --> 00:48:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] ide godinu dana, je to išlo.

1105
00:48:45,039 --> 00:48:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] I nakon toga se,

1106
00:48:46,460 --> 00:48:48,440
[SPEAKER_01] kroz to vrijeme se formira ovih zbor.

1107
00:48:48,440 --> 00:48:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vidio sam i ovi plus 40,

1108
00:48:51,840 --> 00:48:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] imamo dvije grupe,

1109
00:48:53,139 --> 00:48:54,900
[SPEAKER_01] to 40 i plus 40,

1110
00:48:54,900 --> 00:48:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] rekao, i njima treba.

1111
00:48:56,559 --> 00:48:57,659
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su žedni.

1112
00:48:57,659 --> 00:48:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, kako ćemo, šta ćemo,

1113
00:48:59,840 --> 00:49:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] oje FES, Frama,

1114
00:49:01,800 --> 00:49:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne može, Frama, ovi su u godinama.

1115
00:49:04,619 --> 00:49:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, ajmo mi jednu molitvenu zajednicu.

1116
00:49:06,559 --> 00:49:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] Onda sam otišao od Zagreb

1117
00:49:08,320 --> 00:49:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] i sjećam se gore u

1118
00:49:09,719 --> 00:49:12,019
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj Hrvatskom institutu

1119
00:49:12,019 --> 00:49:13,280
[SPEAKER_01] za liturgijski pastoral.

1120
00:49:13,280 --> 00:49:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ja govorim, žena, daj mi 90 časoslova.

1121
00:49:15,980 --> 00:49:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nekako sam dugo razmatrao,

1122
00:49:18,019 --> 00:49:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] bože, evo, šta ću, kako ću.

1123
00:49:19,539 --> 00:49:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] I rekao, ide mi,

1124
00:49:21,019 --> 00:49:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću njih naučiti molitve crkve.

1125
00:49:23,219 --> 00:49:25,760
[SPEAKER_01] Časoslovi, božanski časoslov,

1126
00:49:25,760 --> 00:49:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] liturgija časova,

1127
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] i zaista se to lijepo prihvatili.

1128
00:49:28,920 --> 00:49:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, žena, gdje ide u časoslovi,

1129
00:49:30,960 --> 00:49:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] ova prodavačica, ja govorim u šitavsku.

1130
00:49:32,800 --> 00:49:34,179
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, pa si kad vam čuli za to.

1131
00:49:34,179 --> 00:49:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao, nisu, ali sad će čuti.

1132
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ovaj, evo, to je jedna jako lijepa

1133
00:49:39,440 --> 00:49:42,000
