1134
00:49:42,000 --> 00:49:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] sudjeluje cijelo tijelo crkve,

1135
00:49:44,880 --> 00:49:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] kada se, kada molimo, evo,

1136
00:49:46,480 --> 00:49:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] božanski časoslov, ti isto to dobro znaš,

1137
00:49:48,820 --> 00:49:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] evo, tu si u EFES-u,

1138
00:49:50,679 --> 00:49:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] član si, tako da znaš kako je da ta molitva.

1139
00:49:54,179 --> 00:49:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] I, evo, Bogu hvala,

1140
00:49:55,539 --> 00:49:57,079
[SPEAKER_01] da se od napredu ide dobro,

1141
00:49:57,079 --> 00:49:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali idemo korak po korak,

1142
00:49:58,539 --> 00:49:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] ne treba žuriti,

1143
00:49:59,480 --> 00:50:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo, vidit ćemo,

1144
