[SPEAKER_01] hoće li se vratiti nazad,

1148
00:50:06,820 --> 00:50:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] u Božije ruke, evo,

1149
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] ko što i sada sam otišao gore,

1150
00:50:10,159 --> 00:50:11,820
[SPEAKER_01] u Božijom provjednošću,

1151
00:50:11,820 --> 00:50:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] tek sam nakon nekog vremena

1152
00:50:14,659 --> 00:50:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] shvatio svoj smisao,

1153
00:50:15,920 --> 00:50:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] zašto sam gore,

1154
00:50:16,840 --> 00:50:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] u početku, naravno,

1155
00:50:18,360 --> 00:50:19,860
[SPEAKER_01] ideš u nepoznato,

1156
00:50:19,860 --> 00:50:22,139
[SPEAKER_01] tako će gospodin provjediti zadalje,

1157
00:50:22,139 --> 00:50:23,659
