1162
00:50:29,639 --> 00:50:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] I, upravo, spomenuo Međugorje i Mladifest,

1163
00:50:32,460 --> 00:50:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] mi, evo, snimamo vrijeme,

1164
00:50:33,619 --> 00:50:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] Mladifest,

1165
00:50:34,719 --> 00:50:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] a, upravo, je nekako,

1166
00:50:35,719 --> 00:50:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] Međugorje pokazate koliko je,

1167
00:50:38,159 --> 00:50:41,280
