[SPEAKER_00] iz Koreje, iz Kine,

1173
00:50:50,039 --> 00:50:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz nekih afričkih zemalja,

1174
00:50:51,980 --> 00:50:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, no, dakle,

1175
00:50:52,719 --> 00:50:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] sve ljudi ne dolaze ovdje u Međugorje,

1176
00:50:55,239 --> 00:50:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] ono, baš neki pokazate.

1177
00:50:56,659 --> 00:50:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, tako je,

1178
