[SPEAKER_01] veliko je uvijek u Božijim očima,

1193
00:51:22,860 --> 00:51:24,179
[SPEAKER_01] svako obraćenje je veliko,

1194
00:51:24,179 --> 00:51:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

1195
