[SPEAKER_01] da se Gospod kazala u Međugorju,

1203
00:51:37,579 --> 00:51:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] čuva sam ja možda to,

1204
00:51:38,460 --> 00:51:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali, ono,

1205
00:51:39,000 --> 00:51:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] to mi je bilo,

1206
00:51:39,659 --> 00:51:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] okej, super, šta sad,

1207
00:51:40,980 --> 00:51:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

1208
00:51:41,960 --> 00:51:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] vjerujem da i ovdje dosta ljudi,

1209
00:51:43,920 --> 00:51:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] nesreća tu milost Međugorja,

1210
00:51:45,699 --> 00:51:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] to je,

1211
00:51:47,079 --> 00:51:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako nas je Gospod i nebo nagradilo,

1212
00:51:49,460 --> 00:51:50,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi nismo svjesni,

1213
00:51:50,880 --> 00:51:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] mi nismo svjesni,

1214
00:51:54,139 --> 00:51:55,139
[SPEAKER_01] i zato mi je žao,

1215
00:51:55,139 --> 00:51:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

1216
