[SPEAKER_01] odlazi u Međugorje,

1221
00:52:01,039 --> 00:52:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer je ono,

1222
00:52:01,340 --> 00:52:03,219
[SPEAKER_01] značajno za moj osobni,

1223
00:52:03,219 --> 00:52:04,059
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

1224
00:52:04,059 --> 00:52:04,519
[SPEAKER_01] put,

1225
00:52:04,519 --> 00:52:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] gospodinu,

1226
00:52:05,619 --> 00:52:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa,

1227
00:52:06,159 --> 00:52:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] zato mi je bilo,

1228
00:52:07,699 --> 00:52:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] i dok sam bio tu,

1229
