1287
00:53:22,860 --> 00:53:23,780
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

1288
00:53:23,780 --> 00:53:24,699
[SPEAKER_01] iz Međugorja,

1289
00:53:24,699 --> 00:53:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ivan Vidijoc,

1290
00:53:25,840 --> 00:53:27,059
