[SPEAKER_01] tu ću malo neke stvari samo naglasiti.

1508
00:59:11,099 --> 00:59:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je gledal moj odlazak nedeljni na misu?

1509
00:59:15,239 --> 00:59:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, imali ste već eno sredočanstvo

1510
00:59:18,519 --> 00:59:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] o poteškoćama i kocke.

1511
00:59:21,980 --> 00:59:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je tata od našeg fraželjka bio u emisiji.

1512
00:59:26,079 --> 00:59:30,179
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, ja nisam bio zaglibio sad nešto toliko u kocku,

1513
00:59:30,179 --> 00:59:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali koliko mogu reći zapravo da nisam bio zaglibio u kladionicu,

1514
00:59:34,579 --> 00:59:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] ako sam bio u njoj svaki dan.

1515
00:59:36,659 --> 00:59:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čak možda onda mogu reći da sam zaglibio.

1516
00:59:40,340 --> 00:59:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali s druge strane, nisam zaglibio što se tiče nekih dugova,

1517
00:59:43,880 --> 00:59:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] što se tiče nekih velikih ulaganja

1518
00:59:46,880 --> 00:59:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] u nešto što nema nikakvu budućnost.

1519
00:59:49,960 --> 00:59:52,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ali jednostavno, bio si okružen,

1520
00:59:52,300 --> 00:59:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] zato evo, jako važno, to je poruka roditeljima,

1521
00:59:56,420 --> 00:59:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] provjeravajte s kim se vaša djeca druže,

1522
00:59:58,099 --> 00:59:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] vodite svoju djecu u crkvu što češće,

1523
00:59:59,960 --> 01:00:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] da se uključe u zbor, da se uključe u ministrante,

1524
01:00:02,960 --> 01:00:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] da se uključe u bilo kakvu crkvenu organizaciju.

1525
01:00:07,440 --> 01:00:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako tebe odgaja društvo,

1526
01:00:09,420 --> 01:00:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] a sve nas odgaja društvo u srednjoj školi,

1527
01:00:11,840 --> 01:00:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] onda ti upaneš u neke teške probleme.

1528
01:00:16,320 --> 01:00:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, rećemo, to ću istaknuti,

1529
01:00:19,719 --> 01:00:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] jer je jedna jako važna stvar za moje obraćanje bila.

1530
01:00:23,320 --> 01:00:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz srednju školu, kažem, bio sam u društvu

1531
01:00:27,480 --> 01:00:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] koje je promicalo sve one stvari

1532
01:00:30,019 --> 01:00:31,780
[SPEAKER_01] koje nisu dobre, vrednote.

1533
01:00:31,780 --> 01:00:37,139
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, to je odnosi prije braka,

1534
01:00:37,139 --> 01:00:40,139
[SPEAKER_01] koje su, naravno, tek kaznje je shvatio

1535
01:00:40,139 --> 01:00:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala, nisam ih ne imao,

1536
01:00:42,099 --> 01:00:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali, kažem, bio si u takvom društvu

1537
01:00:44,539 --> 01:00:45,860
[SPEAKER_01] gdje si bio pre blizu toga.

1538
01:00:46,320 --> 01:00:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je to bilo normalno.

1539
01:00:47,440 --> 01:00:51,280
[SPEAKER_01] I sada, ti živiš u takvom društvu,

1540
01:00:51,280 --> 01:00:53,059
[SPEAKER_01] ako nisi u tome,

1541
01:00:53,059 --> 01:00:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije dobro.

1542
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možeš biti dio toga društva.

1543
01:00:56,280 --> 01:00:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno se čovjek boji da ne ostane sam.

1544
01:00:58,719 --> 01:01:01,199
[SPEAKER_01] A ako vidiš da još ima takvih ljudi

1545
01:01:01,199 --> 01:01:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] koji želi živjeti evanđijoski,

1546
01:01:02,639 --> 01:01:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] da ima drugi način, da ima bolje nešto,

1547
01:01:04,960 --> 01:01:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako imaš više ponuda,

1548
01:01:06,579 --> 01:01:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] onda vidiš, ej, nisam sam,

1549
01:01:08,400 --> 01:01:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] ima još oni koji su, što ovi kažu,

1550
01:01:10,880 --> 01:01:11,940
[SPEAKER_01] mi nisam normalni.

1551
01:01:11,940 --> 01:01:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje se ne spava prije braka.

1552
01:01:14,559 --> 01:01:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mi tu spolnost svedemo

1553
01:01:16,639 --> 01:01:19,320
[SPEAKER_01] na minimalni užitak,

1554
01:01:19,320 --> 01:01:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] na nešto što je toliko prolazno,

1555
01:01:21,699 --> 01:01:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] što je nevažno.

1556
01:01:22,539 --> 01:01:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] A Bog nam je dao dar spolnost

1557
01:01:24,559 --> 01:01:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] da njemu uživamo.

1558
01:01:25,460 --> 01:01:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zna se kada.

1559
01:01:26,800 --> 01:01:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] Zna se kada.

1560
01:01:28,260 --> 01:01:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] To isto je jedan veliki problem gore

1561
01:01:29,880 --> 01:01:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] u Švitarsku,

1562
01:01:30,739 --> 01:01:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo nećemo sada skakat s teme

1563
01:01:32,460 --> 01:01:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] na temu,

1564
01:01:32,800 --> 01:01:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] ostaćemo na ovome.

1565
01:01:34,679 --> 01:01:36,760
[SPEAKER_01] Samo želim reći u kakvom sam okruženju bio

1566
01:01:36,760 --> 01:01:37,559
[SPEAKER_01] odrastao.

1567
01:01:37,559 --> 01:01:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ne krivim te ljude,

1568
01:01:39,440 --> 01:01:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] naravno.

1569
01:01:40,460 --> 01:01:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] Takvo je društvo,

1570
01:01:42,260 --> 01:01:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] imaš svoje razredi,

1571
01:01:43,239 --> 01:01:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] ideš u takav razredi,

1572
01:01:44,400 --> 01:01:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] ono, promičio se takve stvari

1573
01:01:45,920 --> 01:01:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] ko me nije dano,

1574
01:01:48,079 --> 01:01:49,219
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno,

1575
01:01:49,219 --> 01:01:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] ne može dati drugima.

1576
01:01:51,420 --> 01:01:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] I odrastao sam u Mostaru,

1577
01:01:54,079 --> 01:01:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] evo, dole sam išao u srednju

1578
01:01:55,420 --> 01:01:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] građevinsku školu,

1579
01:01:57,500 --> 01:01:59,559
[SPEAKER_01] sve te neke stvari su bile blizu mene,

1580
01:01:59,559 --> 01:02:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] koje nisu bile dobre.

1581
01:02:00,980 --> 01:02:03,679
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, najviše ću istaknuti tu u kladionicu.

1582
01:02:03,679 --> 01:02:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vam nedjeljom,

1583
01:02:04,880 --> 01:02:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek naravno bio na svetoj misi,

1584
01:02:07,579 --> 01:02:08,820
[SPEAKER_01] jer sam morao.

1585
01:02:08,820 --> 01:02:12,019
[SPEAKER_01] I nije to bila nešto iz moje ljubavi

1586
01:02:12,019 --> 01:02:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] prema juharistiji,

1587
01:02:12,960 --> 01:02:14,820
[SPEAKER_01] koju danas toliko zaista osjećam.

1588
01:02:14,820 --> 01:02:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, ono,

1589
01:02:16,039 --> 01:02:19,460
[SPEAKER_01] ako želite recept za svetost,

1590
01:02:19,460 --> 01:02:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] samo svaki dan idete na misu.

1591
01:02:21,440 --> 01:02:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem ljudima nekad,

1592
01:02:22,460 --> 01:02:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] teško mol, teško,

1593
01:02:23,920 --> 01:02:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] govorim ja, ok,

1594
01:02:24,920 --> 01:02:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] sve to beskoči.

1595
01:02:26,639 --> 01:02:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je uharistija.

1596
01:02:27,599 --> 01:02:30,559
[SPEAKER_01] O, kad bi znali veličinu toga.

1597
01:02:30,559 --> 01:02:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kad bi znali.

1598
01:02:32,079 --> 01:02:35,820
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je sve ta misa,

1599
01:02:35,820 --> 01:02:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] sve ta,

1600
01:02:37,019 --> 01:02:37,719
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to,

1601
01:02:37,719 --> 01:02:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] već,

1602
01:02:38,460 --> 01:02:40,320
[SPEAKER_01] živjeti nebo na zemlji.

1603
01:02:40,320 --> 01:02:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ne moraš čekati nebo.

1604
01:02:41,519 --> 01:02:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, imaš ga čovječe tu.

1605
01:02:42,980 --> 01:02:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan,

1606
01:02:43,900 --> 01:02:45,360
[SPEAKER_01] Krist dolazi na oltar.

1607
01:02:45,360 --> 01:02:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] I tebi se daruje.

1608
01:02:46,440 --> 01:02:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tada to nisam tako osvaćao.

1609
01:02:49,460 --> 01:02:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] I kažem, evo, srednja škola je tako protekla.

1610
01:02:52,380 --> 01:02:54,480
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, srednja škola,

1611
01:02:54,480 --> 01:02:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] ideš na fakultet,

1612
01:02:55,659 --> 01:02:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze novi ljudi,

1613
01:02:56,420 --> 01:02:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] nova društva.

1614
01:02:57,159 --> 01:02:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] I,

1615
01:02:59,019 --> 01:03:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] tkro srednju školu,

1616
01:03:00,039 --> 01:03:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] cijelo vrijeme,

1617
01:03:00,699 --> 01:03:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ja i sa svojim društvom,

1618
01:03:02,079 --> 01:03:02,739
[SPEAKER_01] koje je bilo,

1619
01:03:02,739 --> 01:03:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] kažem,

1620
01:03:03,760 --> 01:03:04,519
[SPEAKER_01] iza sve te mise,

1621
01:03:04,519 --> 01:03:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] u kladioncu.

1622
01:03:05,519 --> 01:03:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] I sad svi je normalno.

1623
01:03:06,739 --> 01:03:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] U kladioncu.

1624
01:03:09,539 --> 01:03:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] i nekad si znao ono,

1625
01:03:10,920 --> 01:03:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom danu i po više listića,

1626
01:03:12,599 --> 01:03:14,219
[SPEAKER_01] znao sam ja dosta puta

1627
01:03:14,219 --> 01:03:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] i dobiti neki novac tu.

1628
01:03:16,519 --> 01:03:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo,

1629
01:03:17,539 --> 01:03:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] to je jednostavno bila moja svakodnevica.

1630
01:03:19,400 --> 01:03:20,820
[SPEAKER_01] A ako je svakodnevica,

1631
01:03:20,820 --> 01:03:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] znači da je ovisno,

1632
01:03:21,900 --> 01:03:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] znači da je problem.

1633
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] Znači da je problem.

1634
01:03:24,480 --> 01:03:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam,

1635
01:03:24,860 --> 01:03:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] sam li kao životu više od deset maraka stavio

1636
01:03:27,280 --> 01:03:28,320
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan listić.

1637
01:03:28,320 --> 01:03:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ili možda u čitav on dan

1638
01:03:29,599 --> 01:03:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] deset listića po marku.

1639
01:03:30,900 --> 01:03:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nevažno.

1640
01:03:31,659 --> 01:03:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1641
01:03:32,599 --> 01:03:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] s te strane je to bilo dobro.

1642
01:03:34,159 --> 01:03:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tu me, evo,

1643
01:03:34,960 --> 01:03:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin izvukao,

1644
01:03:36,079 --> 01:03:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] nisem to bila neka velika olaganja,

1645
01:03:37,940 --> 01:03:40,320
[SPEAKER_01] ali je zasigurno bila jedna velika ovisnost,

1646
01:03:40,320 --> 01:03:42,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji je i danas veliki problem.

1647
01:03:42,139 --> 01:03:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] Pogotovo u Mostaru,

1648
01:03:43,119 --> 01:03:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] znači da sam odšao u postlaturu,

1649
01:03:44,480 --> 01:03:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] preiko skokoje,

1650
01:03:45,739 --> 01:03:47,440
[SPEAKER_01] i jedno radijenje istraživanje,

1651
01:03:47,440 --> 01:03:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] svako koliko ima kladionca u Mostaru.

1652
01:03:49,539 --> 01:03:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] Nijem da je bilo svako deset metara.

1653
01:03:50,820 --> 01:03:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] Čudi moji, koji je to otrov.

1654
01:03:53,119 --> 01:03:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to razara obitelji?

1655
01:03:55,039 --> 01:03:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] A za šta?

1656
01:03:56,139 --> 01:03:58,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nek mi se javi samo jedan,

1657
01:03:58,460 --> 01:04:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] koji je s kladioncom,

1658
01:04:01,179 --> 01:04:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne oni koji vode kladionce,

1659
01:04:03,400 --> 01:04:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] nego oni koji siglali kladioncu,

1660
01:04:05,280 --> 01:04:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] da su profitirali,

1661
01:04:06,480 --> 01:04:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] da su od toga nešto stvarili u životu.

1662
01:04:08,039 --> 01:04:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nek mi se samo jedan javi.

1663
01:04:09,960 --> 01:04:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] Iz Biblije kupi.

1664
01:04:11,179 --> 01:04:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] Doćemo do toga dijela.

1665
01:04:13,239 --> 01:04:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ja sam profitirao, ja, slučite.

1666
01:04:15,099 --> 01:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I, ovaj,

1667
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:19,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja, ako tako gledam, istina je,

1668
01:04:19,539 --> 01:04:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] i uglavnom,

1669
01:04:21,679 --> 01:04:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] što je bilo,

1670
01:04:23,860 --> 01:04:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] upisao sam fakultet,

1671
01:04:26,199 --> 01:04:27,940
[SPEAKER_01] pa i to sam upisao,

1672
01:04:27,940 --> 01:04:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] nekako volio sam kemiju,

1673
01:04:30,159 --> 01:04:32,340
[SPEAKER_01] građevinska škola mi jako dobro išla,

1674
01:04:32,340 --> 01:04:33,719
[SPEAKER_01] bio sam odlučan džak,

1675
01:04:33,719 --> 01:04:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] matematiku nisam volio,

1676
01:04:35,059 --> 01:04:36,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa nisam tijelo na građevinski fakultet,

1677
01:04:36,719 --> 01:04:37,599
[SPEAKER_01] vam nije bilo prijemno,

1678
01:04:37,599 --> 01:04:38,639
[SPEAKER_01] gajde ja će se probući

1679
01:04:38,639 --> 01:04:39,639
[SPEAKER_01] i tu će upisati.

1680
01:04:39,639 --> 01:04:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] I bilo je, evo, Bogu hvala,

1681
01:04:41,539 --> 01:04:42,400
[SPEAKER_01] to je sve Boži prst,

1682
01:04:42,400 --> 01:04:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] tako je trebalo i biti,

1683
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] i upisao sam, evo,

1684
01:04:45,380 --> 01:04:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] fakultet,

1685
01:04:46,679 --> 01:04:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] dobro mi je tu išlo,

1686
01:04:47,940 --> 01:04:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek sam bio dobar učenik,

1687
01:04:49,159 --> 01:04:51,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta kocka je bila još prisutna.

1688
01:04:51,460 --> 01:04:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] I jednom,

1689
01:04:53,739 --> 01:04:55,159
[SPEAKER_01] moj prijatelj,

1690
01:04:55,159 --> 01:04:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio sa mnom,

1691
01:04:56,360 --> 01:04:58,659
[SPEAKER_01] u izosnovne škole,

1692
01:04:58,659 --> 01:04:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelj,

1693
01:04:59,179 --> 01:04:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] danas smo prijatelji,

1694
01:04:59,940 --> 01:05:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] i on je,

1695
01:05:01,800 --> 01:05:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] rekao,

1696
01:05:02,579 --> 01:05:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] on je upisao teologiju.

1697
01:05:03,840 --> 01:05:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] Njegovama je bila u frizerskom salonu,

1698
01:05:05,940 --> 01:05:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] a njegova mama,

1699
01:05:08,019 --> 01:05:09,320
[SPEAKER_01] zanimljivo,

1700
01:05:09,320 --> 01:05:10,639
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

1701
01:05:10,639 --> 01:05:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ucrkode ponekad žena,

1702
01:05:12,000 --> 01:05:13,320
[SPEAKER_01] svako slučajno,

1703
01:05:13,320 --> 01:05:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] zamestite kako Bog dijeluje

1704
01:05:14,559 --> 01:05:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] na čudan način,

1705
01:05:15,619 --> 01:05:17,659
