2120
01:16:20,640 --> 01:16:23,039
[SPEAKER_01] taj susret sa živim gospodinom

2121
01:16:23,039 --> 01:16:26,140
[SPEAKER_01] je nešto što je duboko mene mijenjalo iznutra.

2122
01:16:26,140 --> 01:16:27,600
[SPEAKER_01] Možda nisam bio toga svjestan.

2123
01:16:27,600 --> 01:16:29,979
[SPEAKER_01] I kad kreneš za gospodinom,

2124
01:16:29,979 --> 01:16:31,020
[SPEAKER_01] kad te on zahvati,

2125
01:16:31,020 --> 01:16:33,479
[SPEAKER_01] ti samo želiš još više.

2126
01:16:33,479 --> 01:16:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] I malo pomalo krene fraz Zlatko

2127
01:16:37,359 --> 01:16:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] i svaki dan na svetu misu.

2128
01:16:39,640 --> 01:16:44,180
[SPEAKER_01] Puno protivljenja,

2129
01:16:44,180 --> 01:16:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali imaš ljude koji su tu svaki dan u crkvi,

2130
01:16:47,500 --> 01:16:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] skupa s tobom, nisi sam.

2131
01:16:49,420 --> 01:16:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bojiš se.

2132
01:16:50,460 --> 01:16:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane pričaju,

2133
01:16:52,960 --> 01:16:54,439
[SPEAKER_01] poludio, pomanito,

2134
01:16:54,439 --> 01:16:57,359
[SPEAKER_01] vako, nako, ovakavije,

2135
01:16:57,359 --> 01:16:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] onakavije, treba ga voditi u ludnicu.

2136
01:16:59,199 --> 01:17:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kakva mu je dijagnoza?

2137
01:17:00,699 --> 01:17:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ko svećenika su me vodili,

2138
