[SPEAKER_01] ne bojite se vide njega.

2141
01:17:08,840 --> 01:17:10,479
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki tjedan sam se ispovijedao,

2142
01:17:10,479 --> 01:17:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] išao na svetu misu,

2143
01:17:12,159 --> 01:17:12,939
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim to svećeniku,

2144
01:17:12,939 --> 01:17:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] svećenik se smije,

2145
01:17:13,699 --> 01:17:14,939
