[SPEAKER_01] idem to izvršiti,

2531
01:27:16,380 --> 01:27:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo čujem,

2532
01:27:17,779 --> 01:27:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] na jedno uho uđe,

2533
01:27:18,920 --> 01:27:19,779
[SPEAKER_01] na drugo iziđe,

2534
01:27:19,779 --> 01:27:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] nego idem živjeti,

2535
01:27:21,140 --> 01:27:22,819
[SPEAKER_01] idem evanđelje primijeniti u život,

2536
01:27:22,819 --> 01:27:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] i to je ono što trebamo,

2537
01:27:24,600 --> 01:27:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] svatimo da je Božja riječ živa,

2538
01:27:26,079 --> 01:27:27,600
[SPEAKER_01] da je upućena upravo meni,

2539
01:27:27,600 --> 01:27:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] ne,

2540
01:27:28,760 --> 01:27:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] nekom je tamo prije 2000 godina,

2541
01:27:31,460 --> 01:27:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] bio Isus,

2542
01:27:32,859 --> 01:27:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] živio,

2543
01:27:33,260 --> 01:27:33,720
[SPEAKER_01] super,

2544
01:27:33,720 --> 01:27:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] sve je odlično,

2545
01:27:34,659 --> 01:27:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] apostol ga nasledoval,

2546
01:27:35,579 --> 01:27:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] mi to čitamo,

2547
01:27:36,260 --> 01:27:37,319
[SPEAKER_01] i ljepota,

2548
01:27:37,319 --> 01:27:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] nego danas,

2549
01:27:38,920 --> 01:27:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] danas pozorni u teškim vremenima,

2550
01:27:42,000 --> 01:27:43,979
[SPEAKER_01] kada je hršćanstvo u progonu,

2551
01:27:43,979 --> 01:27:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] kada je naša vjera,

2552
01:27:45,420 --> 01:27:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] koja je uvijek bila kroz,

2553
01:27:46,680 --> 01:27:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] što je čanstvo progonjena,

2554
01:27:48,039 --> 01:27:49,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali Isus nam ne obećava,

2555
01:27:50,220 --> 01:27:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje na zemlji,

2556
01:27:51,239 --> 01:27:52,899
[SPEAKER_01] da ćemo živjeti lagodno.

2557
01:27:52,899 --> 01:27:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] On kaže,

2558
01:27:53,779 --> 01:27:54,560
[SPEAKER_01] gore, gore,

2559
01:27:54,560 --> 01:27:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] pripravio sam mnogo stanova za vas,

2560
01:27:58,119 --> 01:28:01,439
[SPEAKER_01] samo nebo trebamo tražiti,

2561
01:28:01,439 --> 01:28:02,779
[SPEAKER_01] za nebom težiti,

2562
01:28:02,779 --> 01:28:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] za onim nebeskim,

2563
01:28:04,260 --> 01:28:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] ono što ne propada,

2564
01:28:05,819 --> 01:28:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] a ovdje sve prolazi,

2565
01:28:07,500 --> 01:28:08,739
[SPEAKER_01] sve prolazi.

2566
01:28:09,739 --> 01:28:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] I tako je ta Franjina,

2567
01:28:11,119 --> 01:28:12,100
[SPEAKER_01] duhovnost,

2568
01:28:12,100 --> 01:28:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] moj odlazak prvi u Asiz,

2569
01:28:13,619 --> 01:28:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] s jednom grupom mladi,

2570
01:28:14,840 --> 01:28:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] mene toliko oduševio i promijenio,

2571
01:28:17,659 --> 01:28:19,939
[SPEAKER_01] i danas kada idem u Asiz,

2572
01:28:19,939 --> 01:28:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] to je nešto,

2573
01:28:20,619 --> 01:28:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedno predivno iskustvo,

2574
01:28:22,000 --> 01:28:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] i često se tamo vraćam,

2575
01:28:23,579 --> 01:28:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] bio sam jedna 5-6 puta,

2576
01:28:24,840 --> 01:28:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno,

2577
01:28:25,460 --> 01:28:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] i šelim drugi,

2578
01:28:28,640 --> 01:28:28,859
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

2579
01:28:28,859 --> 01:28:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] uputiti na svetoga Franjine,

2580
01:28:30,579 --> 01:28:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji je zaista bio jedan veliki svetac,

2581
01:28:33,039 --> 01:28:34,020
[SPEAKER_01] veliki svetac.

2582
01:28:34,020 --> 01:28:36,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što sam ja najviše pokupio od Franje,

2583
01:28:36,359 --> 01:28:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] je zapravo taj izraz slobode,

2584
01:28:39,119 --> 01:28:40,100
[SPEAKER_01] nenavezanosti,

2585
01:28:40,100 --> 01:28:41,979
[SPEAKER_01] na ovo zemajske stvarnosti,

2586
01:28:41,979 --> 01:28:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] u tim trenucima kada mi je jednostavno možda to trebalo.

2587
01:28:44,880 --> 01:28:45,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ok,

2588
01:28:45,779 --> 01:28:48,100
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji ste,

2589
01:28:48,100 --> 01:28:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne možete neki stvari po vašem,

2590
01:28:50,760 --> 01:28:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš ti i mene,

2591
01:28:51,880 --> 01:28:53,100
[SPEAKER_01] ja oću ići na misu,

2592
01:28:53,100 --> 01:28:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] moram slago reći su curom da me puste čević.

2593
01:28:55,199 --> 01:28:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] To nije normalno.

2594
01:28:56,739 --> 01:28:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] Bez urede roditeljima,

2595
01:28:59,380 --> 01:29:03,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije bilo prošlo, kažem,

2596
01:29:03,699 --> 01:29:06,220
[SPEAKER_01] ali jednostavno ne možeš,

2597
01:29:06,220 --> 01:29:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš pustiti svoje,

2598
01:29:08,060 --> 01:29:09,140
[SPEAKER_01] moraš pustiti svoje dijete,

2599
01:29:09,140 --> 01:29:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] živi u slobodu.

2600
01:29:09,880 --> 01:29:12,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ali meni je potpuno jasno,

2601
01:29:12,520 --> 01:29:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako neko nešto ne razumije,

2602
01:29:13,539 --> 01:29:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] puno duhovnih zvanja,

2603
01:29:15,260 --> 01:29:17,199
[SPEAKER_01] upravo ima sličnu priču,

2604
01:29:17,199 --> 01:29:18,100
[SPEAKER_01] jer svi govore,

2605
01:29:18,100 --> 01:29:19,359
[SPEAKER_01] a daj moje dijete sveć,

2606
01:29:19,359 --> 01:29:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] daj moje dijete fratar,

2607
01:29:20,539 --> 01:29:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] a kad se javi tvoje dijete,

2608
01:29:23,079 --> 01:29:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne bi ja,

2609
01:29:24,439 --> 01:29:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi misle da će nešto izgubiti,

2610
01:29:26,680 --> 01:29:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] a zapravo samo dobiju,

2611
01:29:28,279 --> 01:29:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo samo dobiju.

2612
01:29:29,859 --> 01:29:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj,

2613
01:29:31,539 --> 01:29:32,220
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

2614
01:29:32,220 --> 01:29:35,220
[SPEAKER_01] to je jedno jako važno detalj,

2615
01:29:35,220 --> 01:29:36,819
[SPEAKER_01] evo, iz moga poziva,

2616
01:29:36,819 --> 01:29:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] i tu se puno stvari je promijenilo.

2617
01:29:38,739 --> 01:29:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] I sad i narodni godinu dana,

2618
01:29:41,699 --> 01:29:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] do postupature,

2619
01:29:42,579 --> 01:29:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] koja je ostala,

2620
01:29:43,420 --> 01:29:46,060
[SPEAKER_01] je pričinan događaj prije toga,

2621
01:29:46,060 --> 01:29:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] koji se još dogodio,

2622
01:29:47,899 --> 01:29:50,140
[SPEAKER_01] a vezan je za ovo što smo malo prije pričali,

2623
01:29:50,140 --> 01:29:52,520
[SPEAKER_01] o ovisnosti kladionice,

2624
01:29:52,520 --> 01:29:54,939
[SPEAKER_01] i bingo izvete neke čudesa.

2625
01:29:54,939 --> 01:29:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] A želim ispričiti trenutak,

2626
01:29:56,920 --> 01:29:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] kada sam odigrao svoj posljednji listić.

2627
01:29:59,720 --> 01:30:03,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si spomenuo nešto istoga,

2628
01:30:03,100 --> 01:30:04,520
[SPEAKER_01] pa da ne zaboravim.

2629
01:30:04,520 --> 01:30:06,979
[SPEAKER_01] Točno znam,

2630
01:30:06,979 --> 01:30:08,300
[SPEAKER_01] evo, dole u centru dva,

2631
01:30:08,300 --> 01:30:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] jedna kladionca,

2632
01:30:09,300 --> 01:30:10,640
[SPEAKER_01] BetLive, čini mi se da je bio,

2633
01:30:10,640 --> 01:30:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] tada se zvao,

2634
01:30:11,380 --> 01:30:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] to uvijek se mijenja,

2635
01:30:12,279 --> 01:30:13,560
[SPEAKER_01] kako to što ja znam,

2636
01:30:13,560 --> 01:30:14,600
[SPEAKER_01] jesu neke druge,

2637
01:30:14,600 --> 01:30:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] važnije, popularnije,

2638
01:30:15,579 --> 01:30:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] mijenjaju imena te kladionce.

2639
01:30:17,899 --> 01:30:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] I ušao sam,

2640
01:30:20,180 --> 01:30:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] tada sam već ja bio

2641
01:30:22,079 --> 01:30:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] dobro, dobro formiran od gospodina,

2642
01:30:25,180 --> 01:30:28,140
[SPEAKER_01] i sjećam se,

2643
01:30:28,140 --> 01:30:29,539
[SPEAKER_01] ušao sam,

2644
01:30:29,539 --> 01:30:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim lako sreda,

2645
01:30:31,260 --> 01:30:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] nije čak bila ni kladionca,

2646
01:30:32,880 --> 01:30:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] inače uvijek ja mi uzimu onu ponudu,

2647
01:30:34,319 --> 01:30:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, pa listo, pa sastavljaj,

2648
01:30:35,619 --> 01:30:37,439
[SPEAKER_01] pa hoće li dobi mancaoći li,

2649
01:30:37,439 --> 01:30:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] malo ne zanima me.

2650
01:30:38,659 --> 01:30:39,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ne zanima.

2651
01:30:39,779 --> 01:30:41,899
[SPEAKER_01] I uglavnom,

2652
01:30:41,899 --> 01:30:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] tada me je zanimalo naravno,

2653
01:30:43,199 --> 01:30:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] tada sam već bio ok,

2654
01:30:44,199 --> 01:30:46,600
[SPEAKER_01] malo mi je više taj bingo tada predstavio taj problem,

2655
01:30:46,859 --> 01:30:48,020
[SPEAKER_01] ti kuglice se izlači,

2656
01:30:48,020 --> 01:30:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ti imaš veliko moguće da dobiješ,

2657
01:30:49,579 --> 01:30:51,060
[SPEAKER_01] par puta sam je dobio i prije,

2658
01:30:51,060 --> 01:30:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali tada zadnji put,

2659
01:30:53,720 --> 01:30:54,899
[SPEAKER_01] to je nešto neopisivo.

2660
01:30:54,899 --> 01:30:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baš dodir neba,

2661
01:30:57,000 --> 01:30:58,880
[SPEAKER_01] evo, ja ne znam kako bi to drugačije nazvao.

2662
01:30:59,460 --> 01:31:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ulazim ja i kažem ja,

2663
01:31:00,579 --> 01:31:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] ostalo pet sekundi za uplatu,

2664
01:31:02,140 --> 01:31:04,439
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim brzinski jedan random brojeve,

2665
01:31:04,439 --> 01:31:05,560
[SPEAKER_01] ono koji god zapanu,

2666
01:31:05,560 --> 01:31:07,560
[SPEAKER_01] ima to mašina samotna i neke brojeve,

2667
01:31:07,560 --> 01:31:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] slučajne,

2668
01:31:08,159 --> 01:31:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ja, ok, super, sve prošlo,

2669
01:31:12,300 --> 01:31:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] sada ja izlači, izlači, izlači,

2670
01:31:15,439 --> 01:31:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] čovječe,

2671
01:31:16,800 --> 01:31:19,039
[SPEAKER_01] 300 manjaka.

2672
01:31:21,460 --> 01:31:23,060
[SPEAKER_01] Aj dobro, budmo ja novac,

2673
01:31:23,060 --> 01:31:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] iz izima ispred kladionce,

2674
01:31:24,619 --> 01:31:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] kog rom s neba me pogodi.

2675
01:31:26,960 --> 01:31:29,060
[SPEAKER_01] Pođe ja plakat.

2676
01:31:29,060 --> 01:31:31,979
[SPEAKER_01] Držim novac u ruci,

2677
01:31:31,979 --> 01:31:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] evo, sad držim krunicu,

2678
01:31:33,380 --> 01:31:34,939
[SPEAKER_01] i ruke mi se obojile od nje.

2679
01:31:34,939 --> 01:31:37,640
[SPEAKER_01] Malo me, baš, baš me je iskreno,

2680
01:31:37,640 --> 01:31:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] bilo malo trema pred ovo sve,

2681
01:31:39,619 --> 01:31:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] i juče dok smo bili u Međugor,

2682
01:31:41,420 --> 01:31:41,939
[SPEAKER_01] ja govorim,

2683
01:31:41,939 --> 01:31:44,180
[SPEAKER_01] stavit ću krunicu oko ruke,

2684
01:31:44,180 --> 01:31:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer meni je krunica u ruci uvijek znak

2685
01:31:47,619 --> 01:31:49,640
[SPEAKER_01] kao da svoju nebesku majku držim za ruku

2686
01:31:49,640 --> 01:31:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] i povešću sa nju, nju sa sobom.

2687
01:31:51,460 --> 01:31:52,180
[SPEAKER_01] I bit će sve dobro.

2688
01:31:52,180 --> 01:31:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] I držim ja taj novac,

2689
01:31:54,840 --> 01:31:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu vam opisati

2690
01:31:57,619 --> 01:32:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] kako sam gađenje prema tome je tada osjetio.

2691
01:32:00,960 --> 01:32:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] Neopisivo, to možemo te proživjeti,

2692
01:32:04,279 --> 01:32:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja vam mogu sam ovako ispričati.

2693
01:32:05,619 --> 01:32:07,279
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno, ono,

2694
01:32:07,279 --> 01:32:08,479
[SPEAKER_01] djavlije,

2695
01:32:08,479 --> 01:32:11,859
[SPEAKER_01] što mene veže u životu?

2696
01:32:11,859 --> 01:32:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan papir.

2697
01:32:12,960 --> 01:32:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] On meni ne da živjeti u slobodi.

2698
01:32:15,539 --> 01:32:18,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram doći u platit listić.

2699
01:32:18,279 --> 01:32:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] Mene zanima tamo neko

2700
01:32:20,180 --> 01:32:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] koga nikad neće vidjeti u životu.

2701
01:32:22,000 --> 01:32:24,239
[SPEAKER_01] Neka zvijezda, neko klub.

2702
01:32:24,239 --> 01:32:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je moj bok?

2703
01:32:26,680 --> 01:32:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prvo pošao rasparati novac,

2704
01:32:31,600 --> 01:32:32,479
[SPEAKER_01] onda sam se sjetio.

2705
01:32:32,479 --> 01:32:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nemam još Bibliju.

2706
01:32:34,079 --> 01:32:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja odem

2707
01:32:35,739 --> 01:32:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] i za sav taj novac kupim Biblija

2708
01:32:38,380 --> 01:32:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] i razdijelim.

2709
01:32:40,239 --> 01:32:42,060
[SPEAKER_01] i to je bio zadnji put da sam odiovao.

2710
01:32:42,060 --> 01:32:43,319
[SPEAKER_01] Više nikad.

2711
01:32:43,319 --> 01:32:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, evo,

2712
01:32:45,579 --> 01:32:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] tu je zaista prestala moja ovisnost.

2713
01:32:48,460 --> 01:32:50,640
[SPEAKER_01] Vjeruj mi,

2714
01:32:50,640 --> 01:32:52,560
[SPEAKER_01] pođem proti gladionica,

2715
01:32:52,560 --> 01:32:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] samo se pomolim u sebi za te ljude.

2716
01:32:54,380 --> 01:32:55,399
[SPEAKER_01] To je tama.

2717
01:32:55,859 --> 01:32:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] stika primjerila skladionice unutra mračne.

2718
01:32:57,680 --> 01:32:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] Odraz.

2719
01:32:59,600 --> 01:33:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je do presvjetlost.

2720
01:33:00,619 --> 01:33:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] Odraz prostora,

2721
01:33:02,079 --> 01:33:03,159
[SPEAKER_01] ko je unutra,

2722
01:33:03,159 --> 01:33:04,399
[SPEAKER_01] kome one pripadaju.

2723
01:33:04,399 --> 01:33:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi, bježite.

2724
01:33:05,680 --> 01:33:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] Bježite iz njih.

2725
01:33:08,380 --> 01:33:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bježite.

2726
01:33:08,960 --> 01:33:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] To je moja mala ovisnost.

2727
01:33:10,920 --> 01:33:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] Neki moji prijede su zaglibli

2728
01:33:12,680 --> 01:33:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] i malo više

2729
01:33:13,319 --> 01:33:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] u to sve.

2730
01:33:14,279 --> 01:33:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] I nadam se da će se izvući,

2731
01:33:16,560 --> 01:33:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] neki će se izvukli,

2732
